title: LEGO City Arctic Scout Truck 60194 Building Kit (322 Pieces) (Discontinued by Manufacturer)
features: Build an Arctic Scout Truck with front tracks and all-terrain wheels, plus a snow bike and 2 ice builds with this Arctic truck explorer playset!
This polar playset includes 3 explorer minifigures, plus polar bear toy figure and husky figure

Arctic truck measures over 3” (10cm) high, 7” (20cm) long and 3” (11cm) wide Snow bike measures over 1” (3cm) high and 3” (8cm) long  Ice cave measures over 2” (6cm) high, 1” (3cm) wide and 4” (12cm) deep Ice wall with arch and lights measures over 3” (9cm) high, 1” (4cm) wide and 3” (9cm) deep
322 pieces – Arctic explorer's snow truck toy for boys and girls aged between 7 and 12 and for fans and kids of all ages
The LEGO City Arctic Scout Truck 60194 imaginative play toy can be built together with all other original LEGO sets and LEGO building bricks for creative construction
description: Explore the harsh terrain with the LEGO City 60194 Arctic Scout Truck snow vehicle. This cool Arctic toy comes with front tracks and 4 all-terrain wheels, antenna, lights, radio, binoculars and a loading bay for the snow bike with moving track. This fun building set also includes an ice wall/arch with translucent blocks and sonar beacons, coring tool, plus an ice cave with translucent blocks and room for the polar bear toy figure. This LEGO City Arctic Expedition set also includes 3 LEGO explorer minifigures and a husky dog figure.
